# Challenge 1

1.  Get data via API (any website)
    1.  In this case: universities in Germany (source: https://apipheny.io/free-api/)
2.  Create a table and plot information

## Get a free API


::: {.cell hash='02_data_acquisition_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_1a349faeffe702518557a2654093b595'}

```{.r .cell-code}
api_url = "http://universities.hipolabs.com/search?country=germany"
```
:::


## Import data


::: {.cell hash='02_data_acquisition_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_59f2f098cb718c2fca5eda51c5a7be01'}

```{.r .cell-code}
response = GET(api_url)
data = content(response, as = "text")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr}
```
#> No encoding supplied: defaulting to UTF-8.
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
data_list = fromJSON(data)
```
:::
